data.description: Super cute 2 bedroom home in a quiet, well kept neighborhood.  There are beautiful hardwood floors in the living room and bedrooms.  There is also a partially finished basement with an egress window. a family room and fireplace, plus a half bath!  You will love the workshop room and lots of storage space.  The garage provides extra storage for your outdoor equipment and car.  And the backyard backs up to woods!  Call Cindy Artis at 269-420-1265 for your personal tour!
